{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784786190621,"sessionID":"ses_07275e3edffeaO0otv0k6f0Vff","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7a12904fe63a40ee9f922fe1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0101-system-deep-loop-deep-alignment-multi-executor/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep-review-dashboard.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0101-system-deep-loop-deep-alignment-multi-executor/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep-review-dashboard.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: title: Deep Review Dashboard\n3: description: Auto-generated review session overview, refreshed after each iteration from JSONL state and strategy.\n4: trigger_phrases:\n5:   - \"deep review dashboard\"\n6:   - \"review session overview\"\n7:   - \"review findings summary\"\n8:   - \"review coverage trend\"\n9: importance_tier: normal\n10: contextType: general\n11: version: 1.11.0.15\n12: ---\n13: \n14: # Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n15: \n16: Auto-generated summary of the current review session, regenerated after every iteration evaluation from JSONL state and strategy. Never edited manually.\n17: \n18: ## 1. OVERVIEW\n19: \n20: ### Purpose\n21: \n22: Provides a compact, human-readable summary of the current review session. Serves three roles:\n23: 1. **Observability**, quick status check during long autonomous review runs\n24: 2. **Recovery surface**, second recovery channel alongside JSONL after context compaction\n25: 3. **Resume decision**, in confirm mode, shown to user before resume/restart choice\n26: \n27: ### Usage\n28: \n29: - **Location:** `{artifact_dir}/deep-review-dashboard.md`\n30: - **Generated by:** Orchestrator (step_generate_dashboard in YAML workflow)\n31: - **Data sources:** `deep-review-state.jsonl` + `deep-review-strategy.md` + `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n32: - **Protection:** `auto-generated`, overwritten each iteration, never manually edited\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## 2. STATUS\n37: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n38: - Target: [from config.reviewTarget]\n39: - Target Type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n40: - Started: [from config.createdAt]\n41: - Session: [from config.sessionId] (generation [from config.generation], lineage [from config.lineageMode])\n42: - Status: [ITERATING | CONVERGING | STUCK_RECOVERY | COMPLETE]\n43: - Release Readiness: [in-progress | converged | release-blocking]\n44: - Iteration: [N] of [maxIterations]\n45: - Provisional Verdict: [PASS | CONDITIONAL | FAIL | PENDING]\n46: - hasAdvisories: [true | false]\n47: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n48: \n49: ---\n50: \n51: ## 2A. DIMENSION EXPANSION\n52: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n53: - Completed pivots: 0\n54: - Failed pivots: 0\n55: - Audited overrides: 0\n56: - Swept: none yet\n57: - Pivot lineage: none yet\n58: - Remaining frontier: none recorded\n59: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ## 3. FINDINGS SUMMARY\n64: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n65: - **P0 (Critical):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n66: - **P1 (Major):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n67: - **P2 (Minor):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n68: - **Repeated findings:** [N]\n69: - **Dimensions covered:** [correctness, security, traceability, maintainability]\n70: - **Convergence score:** [0.00-1.00]\n71: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## 4. PROGRESS\n76: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n77: \n78: | # | Focus | Files | Dimensions | New P0/P1/P2 | Ratio | Status |\n79: |---|-------|-------|------------|---------------|-------|--------|\n80: | [per iteration from JSONL] |\n81: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## 5. COVERAGE\n86: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n87: - Files reviewed: [X] / [Y] total\n88: - Dimensions complete: [X] / 4 total\n89: - Core protocols complete: [X] / [Y] required\n90: - Overlay protocols complete: [X] / [Y] applicable\n91: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## 6. TREND\n96: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n97: - Severity trend (last 3): [P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N]\n98: - New findings trend (last 3): [N -> N -> N] [increasing | stable | decreasing]\n99: - Traceability trend (last 3): [pass/partial/fail counts -> ...]\n100: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n101: \n102: ---\n103: \n104: ## 7. RESOLVED / RULED OUT\n105: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n106: - **Disproved findings:** [findings investigated and determined to be false positives]\n107: - **Dead-end review paths:** [review approaches that yielded no actionable results]\n108: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n109: \n110: ---\n111: \n112: ## 8. NEXT FOCUS\n113: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n114: [from strategy.md \"Next Focus\" section, next dimension, file set, or review lens]\n115: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n116: \n117: ---\n118: \n119: ## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n120: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n121: - [blockers, missing coverage, unresolved contradictions, gate violations, high stuck count, declining trend, etc.]\n122: <!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## 10. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n127: \n128: Reference snippet showing what a rendered review dashboard looks like after iteration 4 of a 7-iteration run. Use this as a visual anchor when inspecting a live dashboard.\n129: \n130: ```markdown\n131: # Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n132: \n133: ## 2. STATUS\n134: - Target: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research (skill)\n135: - Started: 2026-04-21T10:02:11+02:00\n136: - Status: ITERATING\n137: - Iteration: 4 of 7\n138: - Verdict: PENDING\n139: - Coverage: core=pass, overlay=partial\n140: \n141: ## 3. PROGRESS\n142: \n143: | # | Dimension            | Files touched | P0 | P1 | P2 | Ratio | Status     |\n144: |---|----------------------|---------------|----|----|----|-------|------------|\n145: | 1 | correctness          | 8             | 0  | 3  | 4  | 0.78  | converged  |\n146: | 2 | test-coverage        | 6             | 1  | 2  | 1  | 0.52  | converging |\n147: | 3 | cross-runtime-parity | 5             | 0  | 2  | 0  | 0.41  | converging |\n148: | 4 | observability        | 4             | 0  | 1  | 2  | 0.29  | converging |\n149: \n150: ## 6. TRACEABILITY TREND\n151: - Core protocols: spec_code=pass, checklist_evidence=pass\n152: - Overlay protocols: skill_agent=pass, agent_cross_runtime=partial\n153: - Traceability trend (last 3): 3/0/1 -> 4/0/0 -> 4/1/0\n154: \n155: ## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n156: - 1 P0 in test-coverage dimension -- review cannot terminate PASS until resolved\n157: - agent_cross_runtime protocol partial: OpenCode runtime path still unverified\n158: ```\n\n(End of file - total 158 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Dashboard\ndescription: Auto-generated review session overview, refreshed after each iteration from JSONL state and strategy.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review dashboard\"\n  - \"review session overview\"\n  - \"review findings summary\"\n  - \"review coverage trend\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: general\nversion: 1.11.0.15\n---\n\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\nAuto-generated summary of the current review session, regenerated after every iteration evaluation from JSONL state and strategy. Never edited manually.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.worktrees/0101-system-deep-loop-deep-alignment-multi-executor/.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep-review-dashboard.md","text":"---\ntitle: Deep Review Dashboard\ndescription: Auto-generated review session overview, refreshed after each iteration from JSONL state and strategy.\ntrigger_phrases:\n  - \"deep review dashboard\"\n  - \"review session overview\"\n  - \"review findings summary\"\n  - \"review coverage trend\"\nimportance_tier: normal\ncontextType: general\nversion: 1.11.0.15\n---\n\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\nAuto-generated summary of the current review session, regenerated after every iteration evaluation from JSONL state and strategy. Never edited manually.\n\n## 1. OVERVIEW\n\n### Purpose\n\nProvides a compact, human-readable summary of the current review session. Serves three roles:\n1. **Observability**, quick status check during long autonomous review runs\n2. **Recovery surface**, second recovery channel alongside JSONL after context compaction\n3. **Resume decision**, in confirm mode, shown to user before resume/restart choice\n\n### Usage\n\n- **Location:** `{artifact_dir}/deep-review-dashboard.md`\n- **Generated by:** Orchestrator (step_generate_dashboard in YAML workflow)\n- **Data sources:** `deep-review-state.jsonl` + `deep-review-strategy.md` + `deep-review-findings-registry.json`\n- **Protection:** `auto-generated`, overwritten each iteration, never manually edited\n\n---\n\n## 2. STATUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Target: [from config.reviewTarget]\n- Target Type: [from config.reviewTargetType]\n- Started: [from config.createdAt]\n- Session: [from config.sessionId] (generation [from config.generation], lineage [from config.lineageMode])\n- Status: [ITERATING | CONVERGING | STUCK_RECOVERY | COMPLETE]\n- Release Readiness: [in-progress | converged | release-blocking]\n- Iteration: [N] of [maxIterations]\n- Provisional Verdict: [PASS | CONDITIONAL | FAIL | PENDING]\n- hasAdvisories: [true | false]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 2A. DIMENSION EXPANSION\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Completed pivots: 0\n- Failed pivots: 0\n- Audited overrides: 0\n- Swept: none yet\n- Pivot lineage: none yet\n- Remaining frontier: none recorded\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 3. FINDINGS SUMMARY\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **P0 (Critical):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **P1 (Major):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **P2 (Minor):** [N] active, [N] new this iteration, [N] upgrades, [N] resolved\n- **Repeated findings:** [N]\n- **Dimensions covered:** [correctness, security, traceability, maintainability]\n- **Convergence score:** [0.00-1.00]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 4. PROGRESS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n\n| # | Focus | Files | Dimensions | New P0/P1/P2 | Ratio | Status |\n|---|-------|-------|------------|---------------|-------|--------|\n| [per iteration from JSONL] |\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 5. COVERAGE\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Files reviewed: [X] / [Y] total\n- Dimensions complete: [X] / 4 total\n- Core protocols complete: [X] / [Y] required\n- Overlay protocols complete: [X] / [Y] applicable\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 6. TREND\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- Severity trend (last 3): [P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N -> P0:N P1:N P2:N]\n- New findings trend (last 3): [N -> N -> N] [increasing | stable | decreasing]\n- Traceability trend (last 3): [pass/partial/fail counts -> ...]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 7. RESOLVED / RULED OUT\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- **Disproved findings:** [findings investigated and determined to be false positives]\n- **Dead-end review paths:** [review approaches that yielded no actionable results]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 8. NEXT FOCUS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n[from strategy.md \"Next Focus\" section, next dimension, file set, or review lens]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: START -->\n- [blockers, missing coverage, unresolved contradictions, gate violations, high stuck count, declining trend, etc.]\n<!-- MACHINE-OWNED: END -->\n\n---\n\n## 10. EXAMPLE (POPULATED)\n\nReference snippet showing what a rendered review dashboard looks like after iteration 4 of a 7-iteration run. Use this as a visual anchor when inspecting a live dashboard.\n\n```markdown\n# Deep Review Dashboard - Session Overview\n\n## 2. STATUS\n- Target: .opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-research (skill)\n- Started: 2026-04-21T10:02:11+02:00\n- Status: ITERATING\n- Iteration: 4 of 7\n- Verdict: PENDING\n- Coverage: core=pass, overlay=partial\n\n## 3. PROGRESS\n\n| # | Dimension            | Files touched | P0 | P1 | P2 | Ratio | Status     |\n|---|----------------------|---------------|----|----|----|-------|------------|\n| 1 | correctness          | 8             | 0  | 3  | 4  | 0.78  | converged  |\n| 2 | test-coverage        | 6             | 1  | 2  | 1  | 0.52  | converging |\n| 3 | cross-runtime-parity | 5             | 0  | 2  | 0  | 0.41  | converging |\n| 4 | observability        | 4             | 0  | 1  | 2  | 0.29  | converging |\n\n## 6. TRACEABILITY TREND\n- Core protocols: spec_code=pass, checklist_evidence=pass\n- Overlay protocols: skill_agent=pass, agent_cross_runtime=partial\n- Traceability trend (last 3): 3/0/1 -> 4/0/0 -> 4/1/0\n\n## 9. ACTIVE RISKS\n- 1 P0 in test-coverage dimension -- review cannot terminate PASS until resolved\n- agent_cross_runtime protocol partial: OpenCode runtime path still unverified\n```","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":158,"totalLines":158,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-review/assets/deep-review-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1784786190615,"end":1784786190620}},"id":"prt_f8d8c0111001LM4vWQszi14nVi","sessionID":"ses_07275e3edffeaO0otv0k6f0Vff","messageID":"msg_f8d8bd67e001qYj6X4iyaIsIBV"}}
